('57497200-1ef7-5b96-9a6d-53fc0eb1ebaf', '78799ef3-7df7-48f3-80db-0838aa200cb9', 'Please ___ these words clearly so we can understand you.', '請清楚地發出這些單字的音，好讓我們能理解你。', 'pronounce', 'imagine', 'travel', 'believe', 'pro (向前) + nounce (說) → 發音', 'pro (向前) + nounce (說) → 把聲音向外說出來 → 發音', '2026-07-08 23:56:22', '2026-07-08 23:56:22'),
